Jimmy Choo Hires Stewart to Advise on Sale, Mail on Sunday Says

-- B y   K a r i   L u n d g r e n
-- 
2011-03-13T12:16:39Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-13/jimmy-choo-hires-stewart-to-advise-on-sale-mail-on-sunday-says.html
Jimmy Choo Ltd., the shoe company
majority owned by TowerBrook Capital Partners LP, hired David
Stewart to advise on the sale of the company, the  Mail on Sunday 
reported.  Private equity firms including TPG Capital may be
considering making an approach, the Mail said, without saying
where it got its information. Towerbrook may consider an initial
public offering if the sale is unsuccessful, the newspaper
reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Kari Lundgren in London at 
 klundgren2@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsaible for this story:  Will Kennedy  at 
 wkennedy3@bloomberg.net . 